    Ominous held his chin, where she had kicked him. He was really, really 
mad now. "You shouldnt have done that. Heres your first lesson...lets hope 
you wont need another one."
    He raised both of his hands in fron of him, and shot out bolts of Energon 
at Quasar. The blue light lit up the room, and filled it with the sound of 
loud cracking.
